Package redecker.mickey.webcnc.types

Class Port

java.lang.Object
redecker.mickey.webcnc.types.Port
public class Port extends Object
This class represents a TSN capable port on a TSN switch. It represents the parameters of a TSN time-aware shaper Instead of replicating the data structures defined in IEEE 802.1Qbv, it stores the information in a more human-readable format for easier frontend processing For example, PTPTimeValues are instead represented as Year, Month, Day, Hour, Minute, Second and Nanosecond.
Author:
Mickey Redecker

      portNumber - The number of the port on the switch
      switchIdentifier - The unique identifier of the switch that this port belongs to
      cycleTime - The TSN cycle time for the port
      cycleTimeExtension - The TSN cycle time extension for the port
      startYear - The start year of the current configuration

      startDay - The start day of the current configuration
      startHour - The start hour of the current configuration
      startMinute - The start minute of the current configuration
      startSecond - The start second of the current configuration
      startNanosecond - The start nanosecond of the current configuration
      gateControlList - A list of GCLEntries representing the gate control list of the port
      gateEnabled - Indicates if TSN is activated on the port
